Welcome to Piso 23: The track that i create when i tryied to combine lo-fi sounds with reggaeton. 

Sometimes I like to listen to lo-fi as background music while doing activities like working, tidying the house, playing video games or just hanging out.
The sounds used in this genre give me a chill vibe that makes me happy; that vibe motivated me to search for sounds commonly used in lo-fi and combine it with reggaeton drums.  Piso23 is the result.
